column5: As promised a couple weeks back here's the story of my trip to the Chapleau Game Preserve.It was memorable to say the least.http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/i...howtopic=45979
Great trip and great report. Time consuming and worth every minute.
WOW!!! Amazing story and Pics thanks for sharing.

Great read and great photos of the camp site, fishing, lakes and woods..... You two get the "Eagle Scout" Merit Badge award for Northwoods Camping and for truly going "off road".....and on a "beer budget" ! Rich B
